<http://www.spektrix.com/nationalmusiccentre/event/143401APGBLLTBJMQTHTVRCKCBVPQHSBG>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name " Calgary Cinematheque & NMC Present — 100th Anniversary Screening: The Phantom of the Opera (1925)";
  schema:description """
	Celebrate the 100th anniversary of the classic 1925 film The Phantom of the Opera, brought to life with a live score performed by Chris Maric on the National Music Centre's Allen theatre organ.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/Studio+Bell,+home+of+the+National+Music+Centre/@51.0445506,-114.054786,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x53717aaa864fd43b:0x7609799479e4d20e!8m2!3d51.0445591!4d-114.0529828\">Studio Bell, 850 4 Street SE Calgary</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Doors: 6:30 pm. Show: 7:30 pm.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Premium: $55 + GST (sold out)<span><br/></span>General Seating: $35 + GST<span><br/></span>Mezzanine and Back Row: $12 + GST<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Premium tickets include a pre-show screening of <span class=\"ItalicText\">Cops</span> accompanied by the Kimball Theatre Organ from 6 pm to 7 pm.
""";
