  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "AE West Welcome Reception";
  schema:description """
	<h2>NOVEMBER 3</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Featuring performances by folk singer-songwriter Taylor Lang and soul songstress CELIN.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Join us to celebrate the Calgary return of the AE West (Artist Entrepreneur West) program. Reconnect with old friends, enjoy performances by AE West artists Taylor Lang and CELIN, and meet the 11 new artists participating in this year's program. Snacks and light refreshments will be provided.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Doors open at 6:00 pm. Program begins at 7:00 pm.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/Studio+Bell,+home+of+the+National+Music+Centre/@51.0445506,-114.054786,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x53717aaa864fd43b:0x7609799479e4d20e!8m2!3d51.0445591!4d-114.0529828\">Studio Bell, home of the National Music Centre (850 4 Street SE Calgary)</a>
