<http://www.spektrix.com/nationalmusiccentre/event/150001AQSTDPGSPJTRGPNSVKQQSSSSNBG>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "ArcherFest: In Violet Light: Celebration Concert of Violet Archer";
  schema:description """
	<h2>NOVEMBER 23</h2>This concert celebrates the luminous legacy of Violet Archer, whose music reflects a vibrant blend of intellect, lyricism, and national identity. Featuring renowned Canadian artists Camryn Dewar and Sandra Joy Friesen, experience how her works continue to resonate through solo piano pieces elegantly complemented with songs for mezzo soprano.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/Studio+Bell,+home+of+the+National+Music+Centre/@51.0445506,-114.054786,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x53717aaa864fd43b:0x7609799479e4d20e!8m2!3d51.0445591!4d-114.0529828\">Studio Bell, home of the National Music Centre (850 4 Street SE Calgary)</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>1:30 pm - Pre-Concert Chat with Janna Sailor and Anton Lindenblatt<span><br/></span>2:00 pm - In Violet Light: Celebration Concert of Violet Archer<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Discounted admission: $15.75
""";
