<http://www.spektrix.com/nationalmusiccentre/event/174601ABBQGHNRPQMCRQRJDPTJBBSSSVB>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Dialogues with the Piano";
  schema:description """
	Enjoy an evening blending live piano and digital performances. Using Steinway & Sons Spirio player piano technology, Winston Choi, Jon Kimura Parker, and Carter Johnson perform live alongside their own pre-recorded performance, creating layered musical dialogues where past and present coexist and voices multiply. This showcase of artists sharing the stage with their past selves is followed by an exploration of the expansive sounds of the piano.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/Studio+Bell,+home+of+the+National+Music+Centre/@51.0445506,-114.054786,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x53717aaa864fd43b:0x7609799479e4d20e!8m2!3d51.0445591!4d-114.0529828\">Studio Bell, 850 4 Street SE Calgary</a><span><br/></span>Doors: 6:00 pm. Show: 7:00 pm.<span><br/></span>Adult: $66 <span><br/></span>Senior (65+): $54 <span><br/></span>Student A440 Club (18-39): $25 <span><br/></span>Youth (7-17):$10<span><br/></span>+ GST<span><br/></span> <span><br/></span>NMC Members get 15% off tickets. Sign in with the email address associated with your membership to have your tickets auto-discount.
""";
