  schema:description """
	Step into a night of smoky blues, vintage swing, and irresistible grooves with Blue Moon Marquee, presented by the National Music Centre and Gateway Events.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/Studio+Bell,+home+of+the+National+Music+Centre/@51.0445506,-114.054786,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x53717aaa864fd43b:0x7609799479e4d20e!8m2!3d51.0445591!4d-114.0529828\">Studio Bell, 850 4 Street SE Calgary</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Doors: 6:30 pm. Show: 7:30 pm.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Early Bird: $35 (until March 31)<span><br/></span>General: $41<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Members receive 15% off — just log into your NMC account and it’s applied automatically.
