  schema:name "NMC Presents: Duane Forrest — Bob Marley: How Reggae Changed the World ";
  schema:description """
	NMC proudly presents Duane Forrest's acclaimed live show <span class=\"ItalicText\">Bob Marley: How Regge Changed the World</span>. Join us for a special evening celebrating Bob Marley’s birthday and the profound global impact of his music.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/Studio+Bell,+home+of+the+National+Music+Centre/@51.0445506,-114.054786,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x53717aaa864fd43b:0x7609799479e4d20e!8m2!3d51.0445591!4d-114.0529828\">Studio Bell, 850 4 Street SE Calgary</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Doors: 6:30 pm. Show: 7:30 pm.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>VIP: $60 + GST - SOLD OUT<span><br/></span>General: $35 + GST - SOLD OUT<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>VIP ticket holders will enjoy reserved seating in the Performance Hall, along with a pre-show guided tour of the Rolling Stones Mobile Studio, which recorded Bob Marley and the Wailers’ 1975 album <span class=\"ItalicText\">Live!</span> in London. VIP tour begins at 6:00 pm.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>NMC Members get 15% off. Check your email for the discount code in our Members Newsletter.<span><br/></span>
""";
